data.description: Incredible Lennar Lexington plan home with so many upgrades to include hand scraped hickory wood floors, spacious kitchen w/stainless appliances, media room with reclining chairs, screen & projector, wine fridge and more. Backyard paradise that is great for entertaining with beautiful waterfall heated pool and spa, outdoor kitchen with pergola. Solar screens, widened driveway, workshop added with AC and insulation in garage, sprinkler system, floored attic space, wired for surround sound, tech shield, 2- water heaters, water softener, and much more!  Fabulous property! In Golf course community near schools, shopping and entertainment.  ALL INFORMATION IS DEEMED CORRECT, BUT TO BE INDPENDENTLY VERIFIED BY BUYER.
